<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. ـظُرْ مَا تَعَلَّقَهُ إِذَا بعَيَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>هَذَا هُوَ الدُّنْيَا كَذَا قَالَ الرَّسُو<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لُ مُمَثِّلاً وَالْحَقُّ ذُو تِبْيَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَكَذَاكَ مَثَّلَهَا بِظِلِّ الدَّوْحِ فِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَقْتِ الْحَرُورِ لِقَائِلِ الرُّكْبَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هَذَا وَلَوْ عَدَلَتْ جَنَاحَ بَعُوضَةٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عِنْدَ الإِلَهِ الْحَقِّ فِي الْمِيزَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لَمْ يَسْقِ مِنْهَا كَافِرًا مِنْ شَرْبَةٍ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مَاءً وَكَانَ الْحَقُّ بِالْحِرْمَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَاللهِ مَا عَقَلَ امْرُؤٌ قَدْ بَاعَ مَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>يَبْقَى بِمَا هُوَ مُضْمَحِلِّ فَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هَذَا وَيُفْتِي ثُمَّ يَقْضِي حَاكِمًا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بِالْحِجْرِ مِنْ سَفَهٍ لِذَا الإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>إِذْ بَاعَ شَيْئًا قَدْرُهُ فَوْقَ الَّذِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يُعْتَاضُهُ مِنْ هَذِهِ الأَثْمَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَمَنِ السَّفِيهُ حَقِيقَةً إِنْ كُنْتَ ذَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>عَقْلٍ وَأَيْنَ الْعَقْلَ لِسَّكْرَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَاللهِ لَوْ أَنَّ الْقُلُوبَ شَهِدْنَ مِنْ مِـ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>نَا كَانَ شَأْنٌ غَيْرَ هَذَا الشَّانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>نَفْسٌ مِنْ الأَنْفَاسِ هَذَا الْعَيْش إِنْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>قِسْنَاهُ بِالْعَيْشَ الطَّوِيل الثَّانِي<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>يَا خِسَّةَ الشُّرَكَاءِ مَعْ عَدَمِ الْوَفَا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>